01:08:27.536 --> 01:08:30.404
<i>and I've just never been able
to exorcise it.</i>

01:08:30.407 --> 01:08:34.776
<i>No matter how many times I tried
to paint it out of myself.</i>

01:08:37.513 --> 01:08:42.015
<i>So the way I see it,
