01:16:33.823 --> 01:16:37.325
Just like David, huh?
Your shining star?

01:16:37.327 --> 01:16:41.028
Alright, listen.
David was special.

01:16:41.030 --> 01:16:44.365
Special. He was a drug addict!

01:16:44.367 --> 01:16:46.300
What the fuck are you
talking about, son?

01:16:46.302 --> 01:16:50.771
