What?

01:17:34.082 --> 01:17:37.318
You killed him, you little shit!

01:17:37.320 --> 01:17:39.787
Yes, his best performance.

01:17:39.789 --> 01:17:42.056
Squirming at the end of a rope.

01:17:42.058 --> 01:17:44.525
